abstract: In what appears to be a humbling development for WCI Communities, the homebuilder said on Monday that it has agreed to let Carl C. Icahn place three directors on its board, ending a long-running proxy fight.
lead_paragraph: In what appears to be a humbling development for WCI Communities, the homebuilder said on Monday that it has agreed to let Carl C. Icahn place three directors on its board, ending a long-running proxy fight.

headline.main: WCI Strikes Deal with Icahn to End Proxy Fight
